## A4) Dynamic Question Prompts (Category-driven)
Use short, branch-triggering prompts:

### Employees question (drives workers comp)
- “Do you have employees?” Yes/No  
If Yes → require workers comp evidence/attestation.

### In-home access question (drives background check trust)
- “Will you enter the customer’s home?” Yes/No  
If Yes → require background check consent.

### License question (for handyman/trades)
- “Does your work require a California contractor license?” Yes/No/Not sure  
If Yes/Not sure → ops review + request CSLB number (or ask for clarification).

---

## A5) Enforcement policy (v1)
- **No provider receives jobs** until:
  - agreement clauses accepted
  - payouts connected
  - required compliance items uploaded/attested for their categories
  - ops approval complete
- Auto-approval comes later only for Tier 0 categories after strong proof compliance history.

