# PART D — Opinionated Defaults (California v1)
- Do **not** auto-approve any providers in v1.
- Require GL insurance for Tier 1+ categories before first paid job.
- Require background check consent for in-home categories (cleaning/handyman).
- Keep license questions only where it matters to reduce friction.
- Use “Founding Partner” scarcity honestly; never fake it.
